Sanguine got out of the escape pod. She looks around and realizes that 
she is in a forest and that there is a lake with a waterfall not very 
far.

She deactivates all of her morphing abilities and reduces down to a 
small girlish bot. She goes around and climb up to to high point of 
the waterfall where she opens a general communication.

Sanguine: Attention, beings present on this planet. I am Predacon 
Sanguine and I come to destroy every single bot related from far or 
near to the Vok. If anyone wishes to join me, you're welcome. Sanguine 
out.
